{"tid":1583994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［行動]全球反極權大遊行前哨 - 自由之鳥 - 遇怪魔我即刻變大個 !","createTime":"2019-09-21T02:08:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T14:11:12.000Z","uid":123713,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"1b83b01636f26f21c1ba3a6682484b634afd71a8","tid":1583994,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T02:08:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">全球反極權大遊行前哨 - 自由之鳥 - 遇怪魔我即刻變大個 !</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">自由之鳥 - 理念:</span></strong><br />\n1.「自由」應該係人類普世價值既核心，我們相信人民就好似小小既紙鶴一樣，雖然勢單力薄，但只要團結一致，就算脆弱如紙鶴，都可以變得強大。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xfShh5t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxfShh5t.jpg&h=0de0bdda&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ofSAPb9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FofSAPb9.jpg&h=2cc1a36b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">922新城市廣場 和你shop當日，14:00會有「遇怪魔我即刻變大個！」活動，各手捉即場學習摺紙鶴，我地會一齊用小紙鶴組成大紙鶴！！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n**大家有時間就摺定幾隻黎砌砌砌啦 ~~~<br />\n<br />\n#摺紙鶴 #罷買 #嘆冷氣 #玩人鏈  #唱歌仔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 另外為響應Enzo Mazak巴打，香港人齊齊參與 #birdfoldingchallenge 作為928-929全球反極權大遊行既前哨!</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iYhkXcO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiYhkXcO.jpg&h=9b11593e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kZGhZKE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkZGhZKE.jpg&h=98ee3f9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oz90cMy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOz90cMy.jpg&h=c5c07b6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n只要摺一隻紙鶴，影相，放上Facebook / Twitter / Instagram / 連登，並加上hash tag #birdfoldingchallenge #929globalmarch #929GlobalAntiTotalitarianism，copy呢段文字再tag 5個朋友，就完成！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">3. 參與928-929全球抗獨裁大遊行時，能把一隻自由之鳥掛在袋上或衣服上，表達對爭取自由的堅持！！<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>同場加映：香港系列《鶴》紙樣！</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sHQ6SMO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsHQ6SMO.jpg&h=ce7cfee6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBy @hthtwu<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YNPfL6V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYNPfL6V.jpg&h=5576bf5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8BhUheb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8BhUheb.jpg&h=715d8683&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rL0Ce0g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrL0Ce0g.jpg&h=e1da04ce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DK03ayC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDK03ayC.jpg&h=377926ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/55bxOkh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F55bxOkh.jpg&h=529c7946&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LLVFXdD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLLVFXdD.jpg&h=f2e50c17&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5txtmFj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5txtmFj.jpg&h=a4811756&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DQp7CdE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDQp7CdE.jpg&h=e9d35d2f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CiY0XdF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCiY0XdF.jpg&h=2c0640bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<strong><span st